PG| ***** 51 ***** |


NT|^B@2
To counter that, some people play Lavinthal which is similar to the suit preference signal you give partner when leading a card for partner to ruff. In Lavinthal the suit that is discarded is not a signal for that suit, but a suit preference for the other suit.|
