NT|^B@2
A high discard means partner likes the higher of the other 2 suits. A low discard means he likes the lower of the other 2 suits. Playing Lavinthal discards, if North discarded the @S10 on my diamond it would show he likes the higher of the 2 suits (hearts). The 2 remaining suits are hearts and clubs.|
PG| ***** 53 ***** |


